npm install express
npm install mongoose

node app.js

Initially from http://psitsmike.com/2012/02/node-js-and-mongo-using-mongoose-tutorial/

Letâ€™s start the server:

node app.js

And add a single document by going to the url '/adduser/:first/:last/:username':

  localhost:3001/adduser/michael/mukhin/mmukhin

To view all documents, go to:

  localhost:3001/

And to add hobbies to any user:

  localhost:3001/addhobby/mmukhin/beer

To remove user by the username

  localhost:3001/removeuser/mmukhin
